{"tid":2090304,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［緊急］To黃店員工：如非工作必要，請勿回答任何問題，以防便衣試探！！","createTime":"2020-07-02T05:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T13:25:55.000Z","uid":219007,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1ca48d5f6d972ddbce435e8c640570db6dae90","tid":2090304,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:46:14.000Z","msg":"呢條法例就係為咗震懾嚇人，所以短期之內一定會做啲好出位嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n根據過往一年經驗，佢哋好可能利用便衣去你哋舖頭食飯，同你地傾吓計套下料，甚至引導你認同某啲言論，一旦中招可能會掃你場，再上新聞大做文章嚇人。根據法例條文講法，食客都可以屬於支援角色，如果佢進取啲，到時真係即時冚店剷。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋肯定一早有哂成條黃店list，諗住搣紙已經走唔甩。所以而家唯一嘅方法總之就係喺工作期間，所有員工如非必要外，例如工作需要等，唔好回答多餘問題，唔好俾佢氹自己踩！ 有人同你傾偈要小心，後果可以好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可以當我散播恐懼，但而家現實係要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲嘢佢哋唔係做唔出，便衣冼人過往成日出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋咁做係合乎佢地常理！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家係非常時期，全世界自己小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891b8382f9f4fe41f2b8a69bbb7d25b127688075","tid":2090304,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01557de51914db987e1e615f05a8a970e9ab0828","tid":2090304,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4a191584050dc1e6704be331ea625cb9cb368f","tid":2090304,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p